### 获取客户列表(不分页)
# @name getCustomers 
GET {{baseUrl}}/customer
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取客户列表(自定义分页参数)
GET {{baseUrl}}/customer?page=2&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取客户详情(包含车辆信息)
# @name getCustomerById
GET {{baseUrl}}/customer/{{createCustomer1.response.body.data._id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

